# .cursorrules 

Styling:
- Use only CSS variables from src/styles/tokens.css (no raw hex or px in new code).
- If a value is missing, first add a token (tokens.json â†’ tokens.css), then use it.

Tailwind:
- Keep CLI/PostCSS flow. Do not add CDN. Do not start watchers automatically.
- Tailwind theme must reference var(--...) from tokens.css.

Accessibility:
- Ensure AA contrast.
- Use :focus-visible ring: 2px solid var(--focus-ring), offset 2px.
- Min interactive target: 44x44px. Respect prefers-reduced-motion.

Page:
- Use block scrolling (scroll-snap) per globals.css.
- Primary CTA uses gold shimmer utilities (gold-animated, gold-sheen, gold-glow).